{"tid":711471,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"當撈侵食巨無霸一定走酸青瓜，但大家就盲目崇洋話酸青瓜好味","createTime":"2018-06-21T14:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T18:17:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"65dae8dbde43bda978f3fdd80ef25c282c8b18d0","tid":711471,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:22:08.000Z","msg":"［你也是總統］貼身保鏢爆特朗普最愛食「麥當勞」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/462397/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/462397/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大國政治領袖的一言一行都會受到國內外關注，美國總統川普被爆料，因為對漢堡的要求太多，白宮的廚師無法滿足他的胃，迫使保鑣為此跑去麥當勞幫他買漢堡。<br />\n<br />\n美國政治新聞網站Politico在當地時間6日晚間發佈消息稱，美國總統川普的前保鏢兼顧問基思&middot;施勒（Keith Schiller）曾被迫去麥當勞為川普買起司漢堡，因為白宮做不出正宗的味道。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，白宮廚師無法滿足川普對漢堡的要求，他<span style=\"color: red;\">不要醃黃瓜</span>，但要多加番茄醬。<br />\n<br />\n最後，施勒去紐約大道為川普買了漢堡和蘋果派。<br />\n<br />\n此前另有消息指出，川普因為哥哥死於酒精中毒不喝酒，但酷愛可樂，在他的辦公桌上有紅色按鈕，按下去就會有人送上可樂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/214923_c18678a926bc863c483f65ad31977b0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F214923_c18678a926bc863c483f65ad31977b0e.jpg&h=2b655c01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來美國總統咁平民化"},{"pid":"9ff220dacef8b9a4dc5f37cc33a966f112beee27","tid":711471,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:23:44.000Z","msg":"發覺巨無霸走青瓜之後好食十倍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/447952/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/447952/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c7aa0accdcfd04eb4c2a152bd685e77f88c205a","tid":711471,"uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":36,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:24:49.000Z","msg":"酸青瓜根本係垃圾嚟連美國人都唔食"},{"pid":"7ca7b52ed087d1d337fb0cf2ba7e0af8a3bb21ac","tid":711471,"uid":62274,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"唔同口味姐手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔使咁激氣喎"},{"pid":"e4b1a4723aae200a7353851d6af7aed31f958c86","tid":711471,"uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":32,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"連美國都出咗套動畫mr pickles諷刺酸青瓜係畀狗食，証明酸青瓜真係垃圾嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fDa9DVuwRDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfDa9DVuwRDc&d=rKuEXMB5T1WbgDAVYwUu1XIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d09f56e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fDa9DVuwRDc</a>"},{"pid":"680c9b933811710573c0bc10ffcbe26c459038c4","tid":711471,"uid":62274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"Btw我會食酸瓜的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c8d3f8f8fe2ef83c66ea2bacec0496d967b94c","tid":711471,"uid":3602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"Make mcdonald great again"},{"pid":"b1a7049766dbada3f60032e55e71b34b8199035c","tid":711471,"uid":4876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:55:02.000Z","msg":"好正喎<br />\n食subway嗌開多pickles"},{"pid":"8d151fcd0d3b8211153de0ea156c4b9a3748328c","tid":711471,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T17:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c263c34c6d3a5f3b71d96695e1806a0f4ec3293d","tid":711471,"uid":14541,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T17:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/011144_e2dc7ed01212ab0973490ef14b2d1a7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F011144_e2dc7ed01212ab0973490ef14b2d1a7e.png&h=d529ddde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我好鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"